Shadow Suite 0.0.2.0 :: Ethical Hacking Toolkit
Copyright (C) 2017 :: Shadow Team <Public.ShadowTeam@gmail.com>
================
Shadow Suite is an Ethical Hacking Toolkit.
It provides many tools that you can use, written
in C, BASH, Python, etc. Tools that you need for
reconnaissance, scanning, exploitation, encryption,
password cracking, and more! Shadow Framework is
the main project of Shadow Team.

What's new?
------------------
1.New Name, new purpose, HAPPY NEW YEAR! <Jan. 1, 2017>
      -It's name is no longer describes its real purpose.
       It's no longer a framework. It's now a toolkit.
       Shadow Suite version 0.0.2.0! Happy new year!

